Newcastle caretaker manager John Carver will be keeping his fingers crossed Sissoko does not leave

Head coach John Carver joked that it would take a bid of £50m to land Sissoko, but a figure of less than half that amount is more realistic for a player who only cost £1.5m when he signed from Toulouse two years ago.

It is more likely, however, that Sissoko will leave Tyneside in the summer.

And the 25-year-old has again spoken of his admiration for Arsenal.

